{"tid":1030310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[犯法企業] 華為創辦人任正非：堅拒按中國法例要求進行間諜活動","createTime":"2019-02-21T00:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T06:45:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"21aa13d5ce2920c81266a43dd4107c5e4f49d1da","tid":1030310,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:40:02.000Z","msg":"華為創辦人任正非：堅拒按中國法例要求進行間諜活動<br />\n<br />\n華為創辦人任正非接受美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）訪問時，否認美國對華為的指控，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強調如果中國政府按法例要求公司參與間諜活動，將會堅決拒絕。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n美國政府指控華為向中國情報部門提供後門，任正非對此否認。他表示，華為從未參與間諜活動，也不容許華為員工進行有關行動，並指絕不會設置後門。他強調，如果中國法例要求華為這樣做，公司會堅決拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n對於女兒孟晚舟被捕一事，任正非認為背後有政治動機，但拒絕解釋為何有如此想法，並指有待法庭作出有關裁決。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否覺得自己、華為和孟晚舟被利用，任正非回應指，認為在中美角力下，華為只是小角色，並不具有份量，孟晚舟也如是。他不認為孟晚舟被起訴與中美角力有關。<br />\n<br />\n今次為任正非首次接受美國電視訪問。早前任正非接受英國廣播公司（BBC）訪問時表示，女兒被捕背後帶有政治動機，並強調美國無法粉碎華為，世界也無法離華為而去，因為華為的技術更先進。"},{"pid":"ef7a8935ca46c54bc4e71f6a6520c510268ae490","tid":1030310,"uid":8048,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"感謝任生提供笑話"},{"pid":"f48ed06ab9cd89b94e75d3b8ab772a892b2bcb02","tid":1030310,"uid":155095,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:43:04.000Z","msg":"豈敢抗旨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epochweekly.com/uploads/pictures/7401/content_613-26-02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochweekly.com%2Fuploads%2Fpictures%2F7401%2Fcontent_613-26-02.jpg&h=f1f2f200&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"133192a6efa5fbf9f8929009756f7e087043f323","tid":1030310,"uid":114692,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:44:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f070b054e4dd096cfad56d7f00d89bf4d6c091bc","tid":1030310,"uid":32816,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:44:49.000Z","msg":"即如果不按法例要求公司參與間諜活動，將會難以拒絕。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0c33c3c0ad02f94fe5ea8b8a242c4810448e77","tid":1030310,"uid":19437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71de8b620076f744a7fbc715fc8886a119a48bf4","tid":1030310,"uid":1552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:47:06.000Z","msg":"哈哈好好笑喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee5e3e951f99e8fd86ac9da377880a7b9fa96d8","tid":1030310,"uid":21653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T01:29:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強調如果中國政府按法例要求公司參與間諜活動，將會堅決拒絕。</span></span><br />\n所以自願就冇問題？"},{"pid":"7ef822aad7c987d6988d060c9cd964b5b9a0e87c","tid":1030310,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"其實佢可以即刻解散華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b55bb2434e469d155e87cb6243b629d8530ca0","tid":1030310,"uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6ee5e3e951f99e8fd86ac9da377880a7b9fa96d8","tid":1030310,"uid":21653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T01:29:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強調如果中國政府按法例要求公司參與間諜活動，將會堅決拒絕。</span></span><br />\n所以自願就冇問題？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T01:41:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中国法律又唔守<br />\n美國法律又犯左</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7f82cd750f75e914e28304a04808edeb09dfeb","tid":1030310,"uid":113929,"like":21,"dis