ormal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e7fc31ef6772d39f57f2b43b2d144cc91887ae","tid":1030310,"uid":18955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"根本就係國企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扮咩私人企業"},{"pid":"ad5cf26c702a8be008df338fa069eaf6e0f6d869","tid":1030310,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.npc.gov.cn/npc/xinwen/2017-06/27/content_2024529.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.npc.gov.cn%2Fnpc%2Fxinwen%2F2017-06%2F27%2Fcontent_2024529.htm&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=12da62c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.npc.gov.cn/npc/xinwen/2017-06/27/content_2024529.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n第十一條國家情報工作機構應當依法蒐集和處理境外機構、組織、個人實施或者指使、資助他人實施的，或者境內外機構、組織、個人相勾結實施的危害中華人民共和國國家安全和利益行為的相關情報，為防範、制止和懲治上述行為提供情報依據或者參考。<br />\n<br />\n第十二條 國家情報工作機構可以按照國家有關規定，與有關個人和組織建立合作關係，委託開展相關工作。<br />\n<br />\n第十三條 國家情報工作機構可以按照國家有關規定，開展對外交流與合作。<br />\n<br />\n第十四條 國家情報工作機構依法開展情報工作，可以要求有關機關、組織和公民提供必要的支持、協助和配合。"},{"pid":"59c00948ffa9e2ac080ce47d5d4bed960b35f7a2","tid":1030310,"uid":39221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"按黨要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5183c31ab230c3674e6af5d4b7d5273a006baf1","tid":1030310,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"中國難得良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5861f2c1b2a688f9cdfa0a869e60bb12ebf619","tid":1030310,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad5cf26c702a8be008df338fa069eaf6e0f6d869","tid":1030310,"uid":51271,"like":